[[File:Friends_Forever_issue_14_Fillydelphia_skyline.jpg|thumb|300px|Fillydelphia于第14期漫画。]]'''Fillydelphia'''是Equestria的一座大都会，在剧情中多次提到，同时也是''My Little Pony: Friends Forever'' 第14期的主舞台，而且在广告中也经常提到。这里同时居住着小马与龙。城市的名字来源于宾夕法尼亚州的费城。Lauren Faust，剧集的字幕以及一些广告中将其拼写为“Fillydelphia”；<ref name="deviantart">{{cite web|url=http://fyre-flye.deviantart.com/art/Unicorn-Family-255844076|title=Unicorn Family|author=Lauren Faust|publisher=DeviantArt|date=2011-08-30|accessdate=2015-04-15}}</ref><ref name="twitter">{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/Fyre_flye/status/312633232740978689|title=Lauren Faust on Twitter: "@orangemeerkat Ponyville was originally Fillydelphia..."|author=Lauren Faust|publisher=Twitter|date=2013-03-15|accessdate=2015-04-15}}</ref>而另一些广告拼写成“Filly Delphia”；''My Little Pony: Friends Forever'' 第18期中则拼写为“Phillydelphia”。__TOC__{{clr}}

==发展==
[[File:Unicorn_Family_Sketch.jpg|thumb|“These were just random Fillydelphia residents.”]]据创作者Lauren Faust所述，Ponyville最初命名为Fillydelphia。<ref name="twitter" />虽然它“未被采纳”，但她很乐意看到剧组“将它用在别的地名”。<ref name="deviantart" />

Fillydelphia的龙镇和所居住的龙在''My Little Pony: Friends Forever'' 第14期中“closely vetted by the show in the script and art, and as a result some things were changed to bring it closer into line for what the show wants to do。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boards.idwpublishing.com/3/viewtopic.php?p=390317#p390317|title=Re: Hello from the My Little Pony editor! (Ask Question thre|author=Bobby Curnow|work=IDW Publishing Forums|publisher=IDW Publishing|date=2015-03-01|accessdate=2015-04-15}}</ref>IDW表示“提供一些龙镇部分的视角。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boards.idwpublishing.com/3/viewtopic.php?p=390425#p390425|title=Re: Hello from the My Little Pony editor! (Ask Question thre|author=Bobby Curnow|work=IDW Publishing Forums|publisher=IDW Publishing|date=2015-03-04|accessdate=2015-04-15}}</ref>Artist design choice and what is explored in the series were combined。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boards.idwpublishing.com/3/viewtopic.php?p=390448#p390448|title=Re: Hello from the My Little Pony editor! (Ask Question thre|author=Bobby Curnow|work=IDW Publishing Forums|publisher=IDW Publishing|date=2015-03-04|accessdate=2015-04-15}}</ref>

==剧中的表现==
===第一季===
Fillydelphia首次在Swarm of the Century一集提及，Princess Celestia表示parasprite在那里成灾。

===第二季===
[[File:Rainbow_Dash_over_1000_S2E22.png|thumb|Fillydelphia的记录于[[Hurricane Fluttershy]]。]]在A Friend in Deed中，Cranky Doodle Donkey对Pinkie Pie表示在他周游Equestria的途中于Fillydelphia获得了一个红色的饰品。在It's About Time中，Rainbow Dash对Twilight Sparkle说“从Fillydelphia和Las Pegasus带来了安全的消息。”在Hurricane Fluttershy中，Rainbow Dash提到Fillydelphia去年以910翼力的风速极速打破了输送记录。

===第三季===
在Apple Family Reunion中，苹果家族成员回复Sweet Apple Acres聚会的来信中提到了Fillydelphia。在Games Ponies Play一集，RD的回忆中Fillydelphia被选为往届Equestria Games的主办地.

===第四季===
Pinkie Pride和Twilight's Kingdom - Part 2两集中，Fillydelphia在广告里的Equestria地图上有出现但没有被标明名称。Testing Testing 1, 2, 3一集中，Applejack提到Granny Smith还小的时候在Fillydelphia发现了第一个青苹果。Inspiration Manifestation一集中，Rarity表示Fillydelphia是她“施展才华”的地方之一。

